{
  "texts": [
    "d. You should try and convince the other player to agree on a design that is close to your preference.",
    "For example, you can try and explain why the design you prefer might be better. ii.",
    "At the same time, it is also important to understand the other player's preference.",
    "Knowing that can help you talk about the pros and cons of each design. iii.",
    "You can also discuss what adjustments can be made such that the final design satisfies the preferences of both the players."
  ]
}